Subject: [PATCH] cgroup-v1: add disabled controller check in
 cgroup1_parse_param()
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
References: bnc#1012628
